        "included": "Edit-route recovery; schedule, location, pace, admission, cohort-cap, dynamic-pricing, and cancellation-policy decisions; event update submission; and the success return to the caller.",
        "excluded": [
          "Raw text-field edits are form data governed by CatchField, form validators, and event data contracts rather than separately cardinalized actions.",
          "Location search, pin placement, and confirmation run in the unregistered LocationPickerScreen modal; this surface owns opening that modal and consuming its result rather than falsely binding it to the read-only Event Location Map route.",
          "Generic back actions on not-found and unauthorized error scaffolds retain the shared error component's ownership; successful save feedback and caller pop are lifecycle effects rather than user actions."
        ]
      },
